@startuml reception-allowlist-state
' Context: reception
' SDD: PROM-RECEPTION-FILTER, SYS-RECEPTION
' Revision: 2026-07-18

title Reception — ReceptionAllowlistController state machine

state Loading : isLoading = true
state Ready : allowedPeople in memory\nisLoading = false

[*] --> Loading : LoadAllowlist\n[constructor]

Loading --> Ready : AllowlistLoaded
Loading --> Ready : AllowlistLoadFailed\n[error set]

Ready --> Ready : SetSearchQuery\n/ filteredAllowedPeople
Ready --> Ready : AddAllowedProfile\n/ reload (skip self|dup)
Ready --> Ready : RemoveAllowedPerson\n/ reload

note right of Ready
  allowedPeople.isEmpty → UI Empty
  (copy informativo, stesso stato Ready)
end note

@enduml
